videos.description: A fan in Boston hurls a water bottle at Kyrie Irving's head that just misses as he is leaving the floor after the Nets' Game 4 win.

videos.description: Kevin Durant implores the fans to have some respect for the players as human beings after a water bottle is flung at Kyrie Irving.

videos.headline: KD on Kyrie water bottle incident: 'Fans got to grow up'

videos.description: Kevin Durant goes off for 42 points, Kyrie Irving scores 39 points and snags 11 rebounds, and James Harden puts up 23 points and dishes a playoff career-high 18 assists as the Nets win Game 4 141-126.
